  "Oxygen": "",
  "Carbon": "",
  "Hydrogen": "",
  "Helium": "",
  "Hydrogen is unique in having named isotopes: protium (0 neutrons), deuterium (1 neutron), and tritium (2 neutrons, radioactive).": "",
